# CSS Rules

All styles live in `assets/jeffrey.css`. Do not create additional CSS files.

## Always use custom properties — never hardcode values

### Colors

- `--ink` — primary text
- `--paper` — page background
- `--muted` — secondary/subdued text
- `--accent` — links and primary emphasis (`hsl(212 85% 45%)`)
- `--accent-2` — secondary accent (`hsl(160 55% 35%)`)
- `--border` — border color

### Spacing (rem-based — never use arbitrary px values)

- `--space-1` through `--space-5`

### Layout

- `--measure` — 72ch content max-width
- Mobile breakpoint: 768px (use `@media (max-width: 768px)`)

### Typography

- `--font` — system sans-serif stack (`ui-sans-serif, system-ui`)
- `--mono` — monospace stack
- No web fonts under any circumstances

### Elevation & shape

- `--shadow` — standard box shadow
- `--shadow-hard` — hard/offset box shadow
- `--radius` — 14px border radius
- `--radius-sm` — 10px border radius

## Formatting

Biome enforces: 2-space indent, 100-char line width.
Run `mise run format` after editing or let the PostToolUse hook handle it.
